ENTRY            F0417   20260225   20260508   20260508       F108
SUBENT        F0417001   20260225   20260508   20260508       F108
BIB                  9         27
TITLE      Investigation of (3He,3He) and (3He,t)- reactions
           on 10B, 11B and 13C
AUTHOR     (F.Nusslin,P.Braun-Munzinger)
INSTITUTE  (2GERMPH)
REFERENCE  (J,ZP,240,217,1970)
FACILITY   (VDGT,2GERMPH)
DETECTOR   (TELES,SOLST) 3He particles were detected in
           semiconductor counter telescopes.
           (PLATE,MAGSP) The tritons were analysed with a magnetic
           spectrograph using nuclear emulsion plates
MONITOR    (13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24,,SIG)
           (41-NB-93(N,2N)41-NB-92-M,,SIG)
           (41-NB-91(N,2N)41-NB-90-M,,SIG)
SAMPLE     The targets were self-supporting foils prepared by
           vacuum evaporation of the enriched isotopes. The
           target thicknesses were determined by means of energy
           loss measurements with alpha source and by fitting the
           elastic scattering data to optical model calculations.
HISTORY    (19911225C)
           (20130711A) In sub 001 AUTHOR, FACILITY were
           corrected, INSTITUTE, error definition were changed,
           ERR-ANALYS was changed. SAMPLE, DETECTOR were changed.
           In sub 002-004 SF9=EXP in REACTION was deleted,
           ERR-ANALYS was added. In sub 003, 004 data for
           E-LVL=2.00 MeV and E-LVL=2.367 MeV were redigitized
           respectively. Sub 005-007 were added.
           (20260225U) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              27
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           30
SUBENT        F0417002   20260225   20260508   20260508       F108
BIB                  4          6
REACTION   (5-B-10(HE3,T)6-C-10,PAR,DA)
